&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hourly Pay Rate:&amp;nbsp;$45.00 -$55.00/hr&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;$10,000 sign on bonus to assist with relocation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
