&lt;li&gt;Oversee cell receiving, inspection, processing, cycling, grading, and matching prior to pack assembly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage mechanical and electrical assembly operations, including cell integration, electrical connections, and final pack build&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise battery testing processes, including cell-level and pack-level electrical and functional testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate execution of test procedures, proper data collection, and traceability of test results&lt;/li&gt;
