&lt;li&gt;Coordinate personnel across assigned shifts to meet production schedules, cost targets, and quality objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain 6S standards, housekeeping, and operational effectiveness within assigned production and test areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support employee onboarding, training, process audits, and skills development to meet departmental and regulatory requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivate, coach, and engage team members to drive performance, accountability, and collaboration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support achievement of operational metrics related to safety, quality, delivery, and productivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
