&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bachelor’s degree in engineering, manufacturing, or a related technical discipline, or equivalent practical experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A minimum of 5 years of experience supervising production, manufacturing, or test operations in a technical environment&lt;/p&gt;
